{"data":[{"name":"104:1","price":"1. Malheur à tout calomniateur, diffamateur,","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6180,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"104:2","price":"2. qui amasse les biens et ne laisse pas de les compter,","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6181,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"104:3","price":"3. pensant que ses biens le rendront éternel.","arabic":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6182,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"104:4","price":"4. Que non ! Il sera précipité dans la Ḥutamah. [618]","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6183,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[618] Du trilitère arabe « ḥatama » : détruire, briser. La Ḥutamah est l’un des noms de l’Enfer : tout ce qui y est précipité est, justement, brisé.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"104:5","price":"5. Et qui te fera jamais savoir ce qu’est la Ḥutamah ?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحُطَمَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6184,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"104:6","price":"6. C’est le Feu d’Allah, à jamais attisé,","arabic":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُوقَدَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6185,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"104:7","price":"7. qui atteindra les cœurs.","arabic":"ٱلَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6186,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"104:8","price":"8. Sur eux il se refermera","arabic":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيۡهِم مُّؤۡصَدَةٞ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6187,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"104:9","price":"9. et s’étendra par colonnes.","arabic":"فِي عَمَدٖ مُّمَدَّدَةِۭ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6188,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah","Chapter Al-Humazah","Humazah","Surah Humazah","Chapter Humazah","Al Humazah","Surah Al Humazah","Chapter Al Humazah","Surah 104","Chapter 104","The Traducer","الهمزة"]}